      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾桂出殿门。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00002",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "和尚带路。校尉的！摆驾观音堂啊！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00003",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四校尉"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00004",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老和尚引四校尉、四龙套、四太监、四宫女、太后同下。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00005",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，桂儿啊！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00006",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00007",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "你看老皇太这么大的年纪，怹哪还是这么硬朗，走道儿多快，也不用人搀着，真跟一尊活佛似的。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00008",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "是呀，您瞧太后老佛爷偌大的年纪，精神也大，身体也好，这是咱们爷们儿的造化，谁比得了哇！",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00009",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿呀，这话你说得对，咱们爷们儿的造化谁也比不了。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00010",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "那是当然的喽！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00011",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，桂儿呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00012",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00013",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "闻听人说，法门寺的景致好，咱们爷儿俩趁这会儿逛一逛，你瞧好不好？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00014",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "好哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00015",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "带路！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00016",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00017",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾桂引刘瑾同走小圆场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00018",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，桂儿呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00019",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00020",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "你瞧，大佛宝殿里头的佛爷多么威武，法身多大，他们都叫什么名字，你知道吗？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00021",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！奴才我知道一点儿。当中间儿的是释迦牟尼，那边儿那一尊是阿弥陀佛，这边儿这一尊是药氏佛，这是清一僧最尊重的三大士。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00022",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "这两边儿还有这么些个小和尚，这个按着猫，那边儿那个逗的是有腿的长虫，有长眉毛的，你瞧这个，胳臂怎么这么长，八成儿他是个扒手儿吧？",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00023",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "哎呦老爷子，您怎么胡给起名字？这两边儿不是小和尚，是十八尊者十八罗汉。这边儿这个按着的，那也不是猫，那是虎。这边儿这个逗的也不是长虫，那是龙。这是降龙、伏虎。那二尊者一个叫长眉罗汉，一个叫长臂罗汉，他也不是小偷儿。",
      "text_length": 107
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00024",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哦，这就是啦。走，咱们到花园儿看看。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00025",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻，您跟我来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00026",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾桂引刘瑾同走小圆场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00027",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "嘿，这个花园不错，也大，也干净。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00028",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "您瞧，出家人早晨起来，拜佛念经完啦，没有事儿，可不就归置归置这儿，打扫打扫那儿，种个花儿啦，栽棵树啦，这就是他们的功课。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00029",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "他们可比咱们爷们儿清闲自在的多。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00030",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "您瞧，那是什么话哪？出家人修的就是这个：扫地不伤蝼蚁命，爱惜飞蛾纱罩灯。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00031",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，桂儿呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00032",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00033",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "你瞧这棵花儿，开的多好哇！颜色是颜色，朵儿是朵儿，叶儿是叶儿。它叫什么名字？",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00034",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "老爷子，我跟您哪打个哑谜：儿子上学未归——",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00035",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "它叫什么呀？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00036",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "母耽啵。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00037",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哦哦，牡丹哪。那棵哪？跟这棵长得差不了多少，也是牡丹吗？",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00038",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "哎，老爷子，那棵不是牡丹。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00039",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "那儿那棵是什么呀？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00040",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "是卖油的不带秤——勺舀。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00041",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哦，芍药哇！走，咱们到放生池看看。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00042",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "您跟我来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00043",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾桂引刘瑾同走小圆场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00044",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "好大个儿的池子！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00045",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "什么话哪！放生池吗，总得大。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00046",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "里边儿的鱼真不少哇！和尚得花多少钱买这么些个鱼呀？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00047",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "老爷子，和尚不花钱买鱼。这都是善士们年年买了鱼，上这儿放生来。您瞧什么鱼都有。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00048",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哦，那就是啦。哎，桂儿呀。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00049",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00050",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "你瞧，这个金鱼多么大呀！哎，这边儿的那是什么鱼呀？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00051",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "那个，是黄花鱼。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00052",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "黄花鱼，它干么贴边儿走？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00053",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "您瞧，常言道的好：黄花鱼溜边儿嘛。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00054",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "那是什么鱼？怎么仨脑袋长到一块儿啦？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00055",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "哎，老爷子，您别露怯啦，那是龙睛鱼，那俩不是脑袋，那是它的大眼睛。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00056",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，桂儿呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00057",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00058",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "你瞧，这儿怎么有荷叶鱼呀？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00059",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "那个不是荷叶鱼。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00060",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "它是什么鱼呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00061",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "它是甲鱼。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00062",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "走，咱们到别处看看。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00063",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "嗻！您给我来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00064",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾桂引刘瑾同走小圆场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00065",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "嘿，好大的撵撵转儿！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00066",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "老爷子，您别露怯啦，这不是撵撵转儿。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00067",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "这是什么呀？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00068",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "这是塔。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00069",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "塔，多少层儿啊？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00070",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "玲珑塔，塔玲珑，玲珑宝塔十三层；层层上，挂金铃，西北风一刮响哗楞。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00071",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "哎，这个东西倒不错。回头你把和尚给我叫来。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00072",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "叫和尚来干什么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00073",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "叫他们把这个塔给我搬家去。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00074",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾桂"
      ],
      "text": "得啦，老爷子，没那么大的力气！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00075",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘瑾"
      ],
      "text": "这工夫不小啦，咱们该瞧瞧太后老佛爷去啦。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03040003_e00076",
      "play_id": "03040003",
      "scene_id": "03040003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
